content.rendered: Our strong, nylon-webbing telltale leashes feature a loop at each end for easy attachment to your MAXTRAX to make finding them when they’re buried that much easier. Sold in pairs. (MAXTRAX NOT INCLUDED) Weight: 120 grams each. Size: 1450mm long, 25mm wide, 1mm thick. Colour: Orange with Black MAXTRAX logos printed the length of the leash. Warranty: 24 month warranty against faulty materials or workmanship. Shipping: We CAN ship this product to Post Office Boxes.  Australian orders: Shipping cost is automatically calculated when ordering. International orders: Shipping cost is manually calculated once your order is received. You will be advised by email the total cost of your order including shipping (International shipping is NOT free).

excerpt.rendered: MAXTRAX Telltale Leashes
